Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:00.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:53.82,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:57.03,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.86,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  reason as against emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:04.60,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  l've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:08.03,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.99,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Endless desire,like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:14.39,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:Such a pain,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.85,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:There is a way E:To change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:18.37,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:21.72,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:23.80,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:28.60,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.29,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Overcome myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.29,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:33.58,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:"A Ahole New World God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:36.45,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:37.81,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:40.81,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:To be a knight D:To be a light L:For you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:41.65,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:42.61,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:No more fears D:No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:43.97,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Everything will work out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:46.15,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  That's "God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:48.47,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.77,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  This is not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.43,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.64,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:Whatever happens in my life,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:59.65,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:59.79,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:Every end leads to a new beginning of rhe next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.50,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Try to make my life complete,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.96,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:11.23,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.84,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}C:Be yourself... Be happy... It's your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.09,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  "God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:17.66,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Find your love... Find your way... For your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:29.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:53.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不願讓機會溜掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:57.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  為什麼會被剝奪自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  與感性相對比的理性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:04.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不得不克服失望感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:08.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  所有努力決不會白費
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  就像沒有終點的慾望翻覆於心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:14.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  理想與現實之間的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  應該有改變時間的方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:18.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  對 就這麼交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:21.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不固定音程去唱歌 也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:23.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  糟糕的繪畫也無所謂 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:28.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我為了唯一的信念而前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我要勝過我自己  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  你要勝過你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:33.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  "只有神知道的全新世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:36.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我一直都是你的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:37.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我知道你在痛苦著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.46,0:01:40.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  成為騎士,成為照耀你的明燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:41.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我們會就這樣閃耀下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:42.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  已經不再恐懼 不再流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:43.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  一切都會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.11,0:01:46.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  這便是"只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:48.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  這不是現實中的戀愛 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  為了你 我願意做任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  無論我的生命中發生什麼事 都會翻過嶄新的一頁長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:59.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不要忘記 我不想被任何人所評說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:59.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  一切的終結都通往著下一個舞台的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  理解走過的人生 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:04.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  變得更強 做到最好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:11.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不回首過去 持續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  活出你自己的幸福... 因為這是你自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  "只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:17.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  找到愛... 找到道路... 為了你自己的人生
